son.&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/rss/edition_sport/~4/jXS2_8m7FEA" height="1" width="1"/&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2014 07:07:41 EDT</pubDate><feedburner:origLink>http://edition.cnn.com/2014/03/14/sport/football/zaatari-refugee-camp/index.html</feedburner:origLink></item>\r\n<item><title>Look who''s back? Giant returns </title><guid isPermaLink="false">http://edition.cnn.com/2014/03/05/sport/jonah-lomu-rugby-sevens-new-zealand/index.html</guid><link>http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_sport/~3/yPMw4YB3WaY/index.html</link><description>Many have matched his size, some his speed, but no-one ever combined the two to such devastating effect on a rugby field as Jonah Lomu.&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/rss/edition_sport/~4/yPMw4YB3WaY" height="1" width="1"/&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2014 15:19:38 EDT</pubDate><feedburner:origLink>http://edition.cnn.com/2014/03/05/sport/jonah-lomu-rugby-sevens-new-zealand/index.html</feedburner:origLink></item>\r\n<item><title>''Dalai Lama'' tribute for Lomu</title><guid isPermaLink="false">http://edition.cnn.com/2014/02/28/sport/jonah-lomu-rugby-sevens-new-zealand/index.html</guid><link>http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_sport/~3/V_KVWoAxvRY/index.html</link><description>The Dalai Lama bows in deference to the great man. He''s joined by 20 other Dalai Lamas, assorted superheroes and a young woman dressed as a fish tank as rugby fans pay tribute to New Zealand great Jonah Lomu.&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/rss/edition_sport/~4/V_KVWoAxvRY" height="1" width="1"/&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2014 12:13:29 EST</pubDate><feedburner:origLink>http://edition.cnn.com/2014/02/28/sport/jonah-lomu-rugby-sevens-new-zealand/index.html</feedburner:origLink></item>\r\n<item><title>''Fastest man in rugby''s'' new team</title><guid isPermaLink="false">http://edition.cnn.com/2014/03/06/sport/carlin-isles-rugby-sevens-glasgow-warriors/index.html</guid><link>http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edi